				\begin{document}$${R}_{\text {L}}$$\end{document}) [13], digital value of LDR sensor along with real-time virtual instrumentation test bench tool [14], and photo-resistance (Rph\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
